Assignment: Homework E3.1 - Positive or Zero or Negative

This program will ask the user to enter a number. 
If the number that was entered is 0, the program will print, 
"This is zero", is  the number is positive "This number is positive", this will be printed.
and if the number is negative, this sentence will be printed on the screen "This number is negative".
*/

/*
E3.1 Write a program that reads an integer 
and prints whether it is negative, zero, or positive.
*/
#include <iostream>
using namespace std;

int main()

{
    int n;
    cout<<"Please enter an integer: ";
    cin>>n;
    if(n==0)
    {
        cout<<"This is zero";
    }
    else if (n>0)
    {
        cout<<"This number is positive";
    }
    else (cout<<"This number is negative");
    
    
    
    return 0;
}

    
   
